      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It runs but has notable mechanical issues that will require attention before it can be used reliably. The exterior has visible damage including dents and scratches, and the interior shows significant wear. Best suited for someone willing to invest in repairs or looking for a parts vehicle.",
      "price": 5000.0,
